<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Publishing Successful</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: #3b82f6;
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-top: none;
    }
    .platform-link {
      display: block;
      padding: 12px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      background: #f3f4f6;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #3b82f6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Published Successfully!</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>Your video "{{videoTitle}}" has been successfully published to {{platform}}!</p>
    <p>View your post:</p>
    <a href="{{postUrl}}" class="platform-link">View on {{platform}}</a>
    <p>Track your performance in the analytics dashboard to see how your content performs.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>The NEXUS Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
